{"chunk_id":"KB-SOL-003#chunk-000-4b0032016c40","document_id":"KB-SOL-003","document_type":"solution","chunk_index":0,"content":"该方案用于把商品资料、FAQ、促销说明与上架规范整理为可检索知识库，支持导购问答、活动说明和商品内容复用。它适合资料分散、版本变化频繁且需要统一回答口径的零售与电商团队。","token_estimate":22,"tags":["solution","rag","product-knowledge","retail"],"industries":["retail","ecommerce"],"solution_ids":["商品知识库RAG方案"],"metadata":{"section_title":"方案目标","source_uri":"synthetic://enterprise-demo/solutions/product-kb-rag","version":"1.0","status":"approved","confidentiality":"synthetic_demo","retrieval_eligible":true,"synthetic_data":true,"public_demo_data":true},"citation_label":"商品知识库RAG方案说明 - 方案目标"}
