{"chunk_id":"KB-CASE-002#chunk-000-2c2107739c83","document_id":"KB-CASE-002","document_type":"case_study","chunk_index":0,"content":"这是一个公开合成服务运营案例：企业的报修、派工和回访分散在多个系统中，导致客户身份重复、工单状态回写延迟和升级记录缺失。团队需要先打通身份与工单数据，再考虑更复杂的诊断与摘要能力。","token_estimate":23,"tags":["case-study","service-ops","synthetic"],"industries":["field_services","property_services"],"solution_ids":["客户身份统一与数据集成方案","服务工单系统集成方案"],"metadata":{"section_title":"合成行业背景与问题","source_uri":"synthetic://enterprise-demo/case-studies/service-workorder-integration","version":"1.0","status":"approved","confidentiality":"synthetic_demo","retrieval_eligible":true,"synthetic_data":true,"public_demo_data":true},"citation_label":"合成服务工单协同案例 - 合成行业背景与问题"}
