{"chunk_id":"KB-PLAY-001#chunk-000-0015819a0dd7","document_id":"KB-PLAY-001","document_type":"implementation_playbook","chunk_index":0,"content":"建议先完成源系统盘点、主键映射、关键字段责任人确认，再做接口联调与异常补偿设计。对于服务工单场景，应先定义哪个系统是工单权威状态，再决定哪些字段进入摘要、提醒或升级流程。","token_estimate":22,"tags":["playbook","integration","delivery"],"industries":["field_services","retail"],"solution_ids":["客户身份统一与数据集成方案","服务工单系统集成方案"],"metadata":{"section_title":"实施步骤","source_uri":"synthetic://enterprise-demo/playbooks/identity-workorder-rollout","version":"1.0","status":"approved","confidentiality":"synthetic_demo","retrieval_eligible":true,"synthetic_data":true,"public_demo_data":true},"citation_label":"身份与工单集成实施Playbook - 实施步骤"}
