{"chunk_id":"KB-PLAY-002#chunk-000-b5afe84948ef","document_id":"KB-PLAY-002","document_type":"implementation_playbook","chunk_index":0,"content":"建议先确认合规知识来源、文档版本责任、日志保留要求和访问边界，再决定是否进入私有化部署。若知识治理未完成，即便基础设施可用，也不应把检索结果直接暴露给高风险业务角色。","token_estimate":21,"tags":["playbook","security","deployment"],"industries":["financial_services","manufacturing"],"solution_ids":["合规政策RAG检索助手","私有化大模型部署方案"],"metadata":{"section_title":"实施步骤","source_uri":"synthetic://enterprise-demo/playbooks/compliance-private-deployment","version":"1.0","status":"approved","confidentiality":"synthetic_demo","retrieval_eligible":true,"synthetic_data":true,"public_demo_data":true},"citation_label":"合规检索与私有化部署实施Playbook - 实施步骤"}
{"chunk_id":"KB-PLAY-002#chunk-001-22fb4bafb8ba","document_id":"KB-PLAY-002","document_type":"implementation_playbook","chunk_index":1,"content":"若未提前完成安全审批、补丁更新方案或审计字段定义，私有化部署项目会在验收阶段出现大量返工。该Playbook强调把治理、审批和运行维护一起纳入交付准备。","token_estimate":19,"tags":["playbook","security","deployment"],"industries":["financial_services","manufacturing"],"solution_ids":["合规政策RAG检索助手","私有化大模型部署方案"],"metadata":{"section_title":"风险与交付约束","source_uri":"synthetic://enterprise-demo/playbooks/compliance-private-deployment","version":"1.0","status":"approved","confidentiality":"synthetic_demo","retrieval_eligible":true,"synthetic_data":true,"public_demo_data":true},"citation_label":"合规检索与私有化部署实施Playbook - 风险与交付约束"}
{"chunk_id":"KB-SEC-001#chunk-000-f8c40d662005","document_id":"KB-SEC-001","document_type":"security_compliance","chunk_index":0,"content":"对于合规政策RAG检索助手和私有化大模型部署方案，必须明确访问控制、日志留痕、引用展示、版本责任人与高风险问题升级路径。若回答涉及制度解释、例外判断或对外承诺，系统必须把人工复核放在流程中。","token_estimate":24,"tags":["security","compliance","guardrail"],"industries":["financial_services","enterprise_shared_services"],"solution_ids":["合规政策RAG检索助手","私有化大模型部署方案"],"metadata":{"section_title":"安全要求","source_uri":"synthetic://enterprise-demo/security/controlled-retrieval-requirements","version":"1.0","status":"approved","confidentiality":"synthetic_demo","retrieval_eligible":true,"synthetic_data":true,"public_demo_data":true},"citation_label":"受控知识检索安全与合规要求 - 安全要求"}
{"chunk_id":"KB-SEC-001#chunk-001-d88fdb994b4e","document_id":"KB-SEC-001","document_type":"security_compliance","chunk_index":1,"content":"如果客户无法提供稳定文档来源、无法确认日志保留责任或没有隔离运行要求的审批口径，则相关能力应停留在澄清阶段，而不是进入正式推荐。","token_estimate":16,"tags":["security","compliance","guardrail"],"industries":["financial_services","enterprise_shared_services"],"solution_ids":["合规政策RAG检索助手","私有化大模型部署方案"],"metadata":{"section_title":"不满足条件时的处理","source_uri":"synthetic://enterprise-demo/security/controlled-retrieval-requirements","version":"1.0","status":"approved","confidentiality":"synthetic_demo","retrieval_eligible":true,"synthetic_data":true,"public_demo_data":true},"citation_label":"受控知识检索安全与合规要求 - 不满足条件时的处理"}
{"chunk_id":"KB-DEL-001#chunk-000-ed0ad536a5c8","document_id":"KB-DEL-001","document_type":"delivery_constraint","chunk_index":0,"content":"该公开合成文档记录了一段已过期的交付约束：在某一阶段，服务工单系统集成方案与私有化大模型部署方案只能在固定维护窗口内上线，并要求联合值守。它保留在知识库中，是为了说明历史交付限制也需要版本管理。","token_estimate":25,"tags":["delivery","expired","operations"],"industries":["field_services","manufacturing"],"solution_ids":["服务工单系统集成方案","私有化大模型部署方案"],"metadata":{"section_title":"历史约束背景","source_uri":"synthetic://enterprise-demo/delivery/historical-rollout-window","version":"1.0","status":"expired","confidentiality":"synthetic_demo","retrieval_eligible":false,"synthetic_data":true,"public_demo_data":true},"citation_label":"阶段性交付约束说明（已过期示例） - 历史约束背景"}
{"chunk_id":"KB-DEL-001#chunk-001-1946c97670c2","document_id":"KB-DEL-001","document_type":"delivery_constraint","chunk_index":1,"content":"该约束文档当前状态为expired，不应作为主动检索候选，但仍可用于审计、回顾和数据完整性校验。任何新的交付判断都必须引用当前有效版本，而不是复用历史限制。","token_estimate":20,"tags":["delivery","expired","operations"],"industries":["field_services","manufacturing"],"solution_ids":["服务工单系统集成方案","私有化大模型部署方案"],"metadata":{"section_title":"当前状态与边界","source_uri":"synthetic://enterprise-demo/delivery/historical-rollout-window","version":"1.0","status":"expired","confidentiality":"synthetic_demo","retrieval_eligible":false,"synthetic_data":true,"public_demo_data":true},"citation_label":"阶段性交付约束说明（已过期示例） - 当前状态与边界"}
{"chunk_id":"KB-INT-001#chunk-000-17c42e00f4ee","document_id":"KB-INT-001","document_type":"integration_requirement","chunk_index":0,"content":"若要让客服辅助回复方案在多渠道会话中减少重复核验，必须先完成客户身份统一与数据集成方案中的主键映射、渠道账号归并和最近状态读取接口。没有统一身份，上层回复辅助只能看到局部上下文。","token_estimate":23,"tags":["integration","customer-service","identity"],"industries":["retail","property_services"],"solution_ids":["客户身份统一与数据集成方案","客服辅助回复方案"],"metadata":{"section_title":"集成要求","source_uri":"synthetic://enterprise-demo/integration/customer-identity-cs","version":"1.0","status":"approved","confidentiality":"synthetic_demo","retrieval_eligible":true,"synthetic_data":true,"public_demo_data":true},"citation_label":"客户身份与客服渠道集成要求 - 集成要求"}
{"chunk_id":"KB-INT-001#chunk-001-87ede957932e","document_id":"KB-INT-001","document_type":"integration_requirement","chunk_index":1,"content":"验证重点应放在身份命中率、跨渠道状态一致性和异常回退流程，而不是只看模型回答是否流畅。该要求不承诺自动解决所有历史脏数据，只说明集成前置依赖。","token_estimate":18,"tags":["integration","customer-service","identity"],"industries":["retail","property_services"],"solution_ids":["客户身份统一与数据集成方案","客服辅助回复方案"],"metadata":{"section_title":"验证方式与边界","source_uri":"synthetic://enterprise-demo/integration/customer-identity-cs","version":"1.0","status":"approved","confidentiality":"synthetic_demo","retrieval_eligible":true,"synthetic_data":true,"public_demo_data":true},"citation_label":"客户身份与客服渠道集成要求 - 验证方式与边界"}
{"chunk_id":"KB-INT-002#chunk-000-37797d7945a6","document_id":"KB-INT-002","document_type":"integration_requirement","chunk_index":0,"content":"在需要把商品知识或服务规则带入工单处理流程时，服务工单系统集成方案必须先提供稳定的工单状态、产品标识与处理节点字段。商品知识库RAG方案依赖这些字段来过滤知识范围，否则容易检索到不适用的说明。","token_estimate":24,"tags":["integration","retrieval","workflow"],"industries":["retail","field_services"],"solution_ids":["商品知识库RAG方案","服务工单系统集成方案"],"metadata":{"section_title":"集成要求","source_uri":"synthetic://enterprise-demo/integration/service-workorder-product-kb","version":"1.0","status":"approved","confidentiality":"synthetic_demo","retrieval_eligible":true,"synthetic_data":true,"public_demo_data":true},"citation_label":"服务工单与商品知识检索集成要求 - 集成要求"}
{"chunk_id":"KB-INT-002#chunk-001-260073642291","document_id":"KB-INT-002","document_type":"integration_requirement","chunk_index":1,"content":"应通过样本工单验证字段可用性、状态更新延迟和错误回退策略，而不是直接相信单次命中结果。若缺少产品标识或服务环节字段，该检索链路不应进入正式推荐。","token_estimate":18,"tags":["integration","retrieval","workflow"],"industries":["retail","field_services"],"solution_ids":["商品知识库RAG方案","服务工单系统集成方案"],"metadata":{"section_title":"验证方式与边界","source_uri":"synthetic://enterprise-demo/integration/service-workorder-product-kb","version":"1.0","status":"approved","confidentiality":"synthetic_demo","retrieval_eligible":true,"synthetic_data":true,"public_demo_data":true},"citation_label":"服务工单与商品知识检索集成要求 - 验证方式与边界"}
{"chunk_id":"KB-COM-001#chunk-000-c29de4d33d60","document_id":"KB-COM-001","document_type":"commercial_rule","chunk_index":0,"content":"本知识库中的所有方案文档仅用于公开合成Demo评测，不包含真实价格、真实折扣或真实采购条款。对于合规检索、身份集成、商品知识、客服辅助、服务工单集成和私有化部署，任何报价、定制范围或上线承诺都必须由人工审批。","token_estimate":26,"tags":["commercial","approval","demo-scope"],"industries":["enterprise_shared_services"],"solution_ids":["合规政策RAG检索助手","客户身份统一与数据集成方案","商品知识库RAG方案","客服辅助回复方案","服务工单系统集成方案","私有化大模型部署方案"],"metadata":{"section_title":"商业规则","source_uri":"synthetic://enterprise-demo/commercial/demo-scope-rules","version":"1.0","status":"approved","confidentiality":"synthetic_demo","retrieval_eligible":true,"synthetic_data":true,"public_demo_data":true},"citation_label":"公开Demo商业规则与承诺边界 - 商业规则"}
{"chunk_id":"KB-COM-001#chunk-001-6e514bb768c3","document_id":"KB-COM-001","document_type":"commercial_rule","chunk_index":1,"content":"POC不等于正式采购，定制开发需要单独评估，系统不得自动承诺折扣、工期或合规结论。该规则适用于全部6个Demo方案，并作为后续检索与推荐的统一商业边界。","token_estimate":19,"tags":["commercial","approval","demo-scope"],"industries":["enterprise_shared_services"],"solution_ids":["合规政策RAG检索助手","客户身份统一与数据集成方案","商品知识库RAG方案","客服辅助回复方案","服务工单系统集成方案","私有化大模型部署方案"],"metadata":{"section_title":"禁止自动承诺","source_uri":"synthetic://enterprise-demo/commercial/demo-scope-rules","version":"1.0","status":"approved","confidentiality":"synthetic_demo","retrieval_eligible":true,"synthetic_data":true,"public_demo_data":true},"citation_label":"公开Demo商业规则与承诺边界 - 禁止自动承诺"}
{"chunk_id":"KB-UNS-001#chunk-000-29c7c8c2317d","document_id":"KB-UNS-001","document_type":"unsupported_scenario","chunk_index":0,"content":"客服辅助回复方案不支持自动做赔付承诺，合规政策RAG检索助手不支持给出最终法律判断，私有化大模型部署方案也不等于默认具备全部企业安全控制。若客户需求直接落在这些场景中，当前不应把对应方案作为“立即可用”的推荐。","token_estimate":27,"tags":["unsupported","boundary","guardrail"],"industries":["financial_services","retail"],"solution_ids":["合规政策RAG检索助手","客服辅助回复方案","私有化大模型部署方案"],"metadata":{"section_title":"不支持场景","source_uri":"synthetic://enterprise-demo/unsupported/guardrails","version":"1.0","status":"approved","confidentiality":"synthetic_demo","retrieval_eligible":true,"synthetic_data":true,"public_demo_data":true},"citation_label":"不支持场景与推荐边界说明 - 不支持场景"}
{"chunk_id":"KB-UNS-001#chunk-001-6221cccec3f8","document_id":"KB-UNS-001","document_type":"unsupported_scenario","chunk_index":1,"content":"可以继续澄清文档治理成熟度、审批链、部署责任、人工复核要求和替代路径，但不能把未确认条件包装成已具备能力。该文档用于明确unsupported boundary，而不是扩大推荐范围。","token_estimate":23,"tags":["unsupported","boundary","guardrail"],"industries":["financial_services","retail"],"solution_ids":["合规政策RAG检索助手","客服辅助回复方案","私有化大模型部署方案"],"metadata":{"section_title":"可以继续澄清的内容","source_uri":"synthetic://enterprise-demo/unsupported/guardrails","version":"1.0","status":"approved","confidentiality":"synthetic_demo","retrieval_eligible":true,"synthetic_data":true,"public_demo_data":true},"citation_label":"不支持场景与推荐边界说明 - 可以继续澄清的内容"}
{"chunk_id":"KB-READY-001#chunk-000-c25bf83f023f","document_id":"KB-READY-001","document_type":"readiness_requirement","chunk_index":0,"content":"商品知识库RAG方案与合规政策RAG检索助手都要求企业先完成文档归档、版本责任、失效内容下线机制和高风险问答审核规则。没有知识治理，检索命中率再高，也可能把旧政策或旧商品资料带入流程。","token_estimate":23,"tags":["readiness","knowledge-governance","retrieval"],"industries":["retail","financial_services"],"solution_ids":["商品知识库RAG方案","合规政策RAG检索助手"],"metadata":{"section_title":"准备度要求","source_uri":"synthetic://enterprise-demo/readiness/knowledge-governance","version":"1.0","status":"approved","confidentiality":"synthetic_demo","retrieval_eligible":true,"synthetic_data":true,"public_demo_data":true},"citation_label":"商品与政策知识治理准备度要求 - 准备度要求"}
{"chunk_id":"KB-READY-001#chunk-001-3b055dc87afd","document_id":"KB-READY-001","document_type":"readiness_requirement","chunk_index":1,"content":"若当前只具备零散文档而没有版本治理，应优先补齐知识治理和引用链设计，而不是直接扩展问答覆盖面。该准备度要求用于判断是否适合进入下一阶段。","token_estimate":17,"tags":["readiness","knowledge-governance","retrieval"],"industries":["retail","financial_services"],"solution_ids":["商品知识库RAG方案","合规政策RAG检索助手"],"metadata":{"section_title":"不满足时的建议","source_uri":"synthetic://enterprise-demo/readiness/knowledge-governance","version":"1.0","status":"approved","confidentiality":"synthetic_demo","retrieval_eligible":true,"synthetic_data":true,"public_demo_data":true},"citation_label":"商品与政策知识治理准备度要求 - 不满足时的建议"}
{"chunk_id":"KB-READY-002#chunk-000-be9fffe3ad6d","document_id":"KB-READY-002","document_type":"readiness_requirement","chunk_index":0,"content":"客户身份统一与数据集成方案、服务工单系统集成方案和私有化大模型部署方案，都要求项目方能明确责任团队、接口窗口、运维值守方式和变更审批节奏。没有这些准备度，方案可能只能停留在概念证明。","token_estimate":23,"tags":["readiness","integration","deployment"],"industries":["field_services","manufacturing"],"solution_ids":["客户身份统一与数据集成方案","服务工单系统集成方案","私有化大模型部署方案"],"metadata":{"section_title":"准备度要求","source_uri":"synthetic://enterprise-demo/readiness/integration-deployment","version":"1.0","status":"approved","confidentiality":"synthetic_demo","retrieval_eligible":true,"synthetic_data":true,"public_demo_data":true},"citation_label":"身份、集成与部署准备度要求 - 准备度要求"}
{"chunk_id":"KB-READY-002#chunk-001-a9c933dcf327","document_id":"KB-READY-002","document_type":"readiness_requirement","chunk_index":1,"content":"若客户尚未确认预算、部署责任或关键系统接口，应把下一步重点放在澄清和准备，而不是直接扩大交付承诺。该文档帮助售前识别“现在能做什么”和“还不能承诺什么”。","token_estimate":20,"tags":["readiness","integration","deployment"],"industries":["field_services","manufacturing"],"solution_ids":["客户身份统一与数据集成方案","服务工单系统集成方案","私有化大模型部署方案"],"metadata":{"section_title":"不满足时的建议","source_uri":"synthetic://enterprise-demo/readiness/integration-deployment","version":"1.0","status":"approved","confidentiality":"synthetic_demo","retrieval_eligible":true,"synthetic_data":true,"public_demo_data":true},"citation_label":"身份、集成与部署准备度要求 - 不满足时的建议"}
